Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:06.64,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:09.31,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:14.48,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:19.65,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:32.38,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:40.84,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:52.69,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:55.98,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:58.74,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:03.62,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:09.08,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:18.42,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:39.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I relinquish ownership\Nof this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:43.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Stalker...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:07.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister Stalker,\Nwhere are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:10.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop playing this game...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:13.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker? What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her attitude completely\Nchanged all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:24.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:28.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have Ryuk's notebook,\Neven if I throw away Rem's notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:31.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my memory of Rem doesn't disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:35.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rem,\Nall this is happening to me because...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:38.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you brought another notebook\Nto the Human World...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:42.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really sure about this, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:43.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:48.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that the notebook\NI gave you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,would end up buried in the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:55.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Ryuk, I'm just hiding it\Nin the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:58.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get rid of it until...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:01.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the next time I say, "get rid of it."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I say it, regardless of\Nthe context it's in,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:07.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it means,\N"l want to get rid of the notebook."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:09.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:13.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Stalker, this is illegal. Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Mister Stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been acting like this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:19.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since she passed out and\Nregained consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:23.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. Does she think\Nshe can act dumb like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:28.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you at least take off\Nmy blindfold?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to see what you look like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:33.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Matsuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Mr. Mogi a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:35.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh-?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:39.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:42.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you apprehended Misa Amane,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:45.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you told her that we suspect\Nthat she's the Second Kira, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I did as you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:50.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I covered her eyes and mouth\Nfrom behind and told her so she could hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:54.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're going to come with me on\Nsuspicion of being the Second Kira."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:56.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't seem to be struggling
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:58.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even when I put handcuffs\Nand the eye mask on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed to have given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:03.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you an autograph or\Nshake your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:06.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I'll give you a kiss on the cheek!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:09.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I won't run away-!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:13.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd made so much progress with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she suddenly talking\Nabout a stalker-?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:23.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Mister Stalker?\NAre you planning to release me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were quiet before you fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:29.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked us to kill you.\NAre you trying to give us trouble now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:31.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who knocked me out\Nand brought me here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:40.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? Do you want to\N"investigate me" or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why I'm detaining you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:48.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why-? Because I'm an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:53.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first stalker\Nwho's ever gone this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey-! Amane, quit fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm scared... W-What is this-?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:05.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it anymore!\NLet me go! Let me go...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:08.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... I have to go to\Nthe bathroom again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:10.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the bathroom...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:15.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been only four minutes\Nsince you last went. Please hold it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:19.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?!\NThat's the only way you'll untie me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:24.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can watch me pee again.\NIsn't it fun? You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:27.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...a pervert-?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:33.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane, let's seriously talk more about\Nwhat happened before you went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:37.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Light Yagami?\NWhy did you approach him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:42.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There's no way\NI wouldn't know my own boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was so tight-lipped about it earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but...now, she nonchalantly\Nsays that he's her boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:52.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the visuals and sound off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:56.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:04.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Yes... Yes, I understand.\NWe're in room K2801.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My son's coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:23.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, I told you over the phone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I may be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:31.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!\NLight, what are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no proof that Light Yagami is Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but... for him to say that\Nhe may be Kira-?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:42.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an act...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you may be Kira,\Nbut that you are Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you trying to do-?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:51.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, if Ryuzaki is L,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:54.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be exaggerating if\NI said that he's the world's best detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:59.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L has decided that I am Kira.\NTherefore, I must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:02.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one that Raye Penber,\Nthe FBI Agent,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:08.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was investigating\Nin Japan when he died...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:11.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one that went to\NAoyama on May 22nd...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:15.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'm the first person that\Nthe alleged Second Kira, Misa,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:17.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,approached in the Kanto region...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:19.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:25.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were in L's place,\Neven I would say that I'm was Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:31.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See... I may be Kira.\NI just might not know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You're not conscious of it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:40.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure of anything anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have no memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:47.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there could be another me\Nwho's killing people as I sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:52.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:55.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there was a time when
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:58.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I put surveillance cameras\Nin your room for five straight days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:07:59.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:04.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You slept normally at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:09.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Broadcasted criminals that\Nyou didn't know about were dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I decided that, even if you were Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:17.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you wouldn't give yourself\Naway on camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:21.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't give myself away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:24.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, up to a certain point,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that some\Nmajor criminals should die...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:35.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that anyone who has\Nsuch thoughts could become Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:38.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! I believe the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:42.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought it would be better\Nif quite a few people were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:46.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, even so,\Nwe can't really kill people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, criminals were dying\Nwhile you had no knowledge of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:53.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The surveillance cameras proved that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:55.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were short of investigators then
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we only watched him\Nwhen he was at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:03.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also not as if we were watching him\Nevery hour during those five days...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:07.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There may have been a way for\Nhim to kill while he wasn't at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:14.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you purposefully come out in order\Nfor this to happen, Light Yagami-?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:20.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we restrain you for\Na long period like Amane,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and criminals who appear before the public\Nstill continue to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:27.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light is no longer\NKira at that point-?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you're trying to do-?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:40.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of don't like the direction\Nof this conversation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:48.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fully restrain Light Yagami\Nand confine him in a cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to detain...Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:55.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should do this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:59.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to go anywhere\Nwhere my eyes can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:03.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is crazy.\NThere's no way that my son is Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My son wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:06.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:07.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:15.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help you catch Kira if\NI keep worrying that I may be your man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:16.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:21.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you decide that I'm not Kira\Nor you agree that I'm not Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:26.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,don't let me free no matter what I say\Nor whatever condition I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:28.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:32.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yagami, could you come up\Nwith an excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:35.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for Light's absence for your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not too sure\NI can so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why does my son have to be\Nthrown into a prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:43.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being stubborn, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be fully satisfied with myself\Nunless I do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:49.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious... Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:54.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. By taking away\Nmy freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:57.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to defeat the fear of\NKira that lies within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:01.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Aizawa, please take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:02.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:31.91,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(458,500)}First Day of Confinement
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,394)}All that's left is to\Nget rid the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:36.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean I won't\Nbe able to eat apples again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:48.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:52.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me off of the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:53.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're holding my son as\Na suspect in this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of whether\Nwe should investigate him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when we were talking\Nabout confining him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:08.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I let my personal feelings\Nget in the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:12.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.\NPersonal feelings shouldn't be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:17.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And, if my son really is Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind of\Nactions I may take.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:27.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I can imagine that you would...\Nkill your son and then kill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:32.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree that we shouldn't\Nhave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you confine me as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:39.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calm now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:42.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'll do\Nwhen my feelings for my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:45.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might\Nsay something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've had Watari make arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:48.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, even though I'm confining you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:55.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep your cell phone on as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:58.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintain regular contact with your family\Nand people from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:02.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't tell Light about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light calls you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:07.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,talk to him as if\Nyou're right here, inside headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:11.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we will give you\Ncontinuing updates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:13.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of the what's going on\Nin the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:20.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am indebted to you, Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:25.31,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,417)}Third Day of Confinement
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:32.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Stalker, I want to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:37.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know where I live, don't you?\NBring me a change of clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has gotten\Neven more bizarre...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so sorry for the Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have any new criminals\Nbeen broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:53.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that Kira would target\Nin the last couple days?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:55.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Kira kill anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a few criminals have\Nbeen broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:05.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but since you've been detained,\Nnone of them have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:09.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's been killed? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:15.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Maybe I am Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, I wanna eat an apple...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:25.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that the murders would continue\Neven with Light Yagami confined,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:28.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but in reality,\Nthey completely stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:32.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like Light Yagami\Nwanted to be confined, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:36.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this would mean that\NLight Yagami is Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:41.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the question is whether\Nhe was conscious of being Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:44.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he is Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:46.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he think he can get away\Nwith saying
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that he wasn't conscious\Nof what he was doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:54.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like Light Yagami...\NNo, it's not like Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.03,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(501,417)}Fifth Day of Confinement
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:03.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it, Light...\NIf I don't eat an apple soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:06.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I just have to\Nget through it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:08.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even if there's nothing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:13.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Stalker, your video won't sell\Nif I'm just sitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:21.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yagami looks even worse\Nthan Light or Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:25.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. It's been five days\Nsince Light's been imprisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:29.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, not a single criminal\Nwho's been broadcast has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In times like this, I suppose it's harder
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for the parents than\Nthe suspects themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:38.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since now, it's almost\Ndefinite that Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:40.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:42.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?! Good news?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no...Try not to work\Nyourself up too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:51.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't accomplish anything\Nby mulling over things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The outcome will remain the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:56.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you should rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in a more comfortable place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:02.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place anywhere\Nthat would be relaxing in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:05.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the state I'm in now,\Nthis is the best place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:08.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the result,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:11.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when I leave,\NI'll leave with my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:13.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:17.61,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,417)}Seventh Day of Confinement
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:30.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, it's only been one week,\Nbut you're looking worn out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:32.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:40.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've come this far,\NI think it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:50.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I know I probably look\Npretty bad in here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:53.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this useless pride, I'll just have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:55.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,get rid of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:11.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:32.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:34.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:39.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I agreed to be detained\Nand chose to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:44.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I just clearly realized that\Ndoing this is meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:47.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me out of here quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We promised that no matter\Nwhat you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't let you out until we decided\Non whether or not you were Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something wrong\Nwith me then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:03.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think that\NKira would be able
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:06.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to operate without being\Nconscious of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember committing Kira's crimes,\Nso I'm not him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:15.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also don't believe that Kira has been\Nacting without self-awareness all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:20.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you are him\Neverything matches up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:24.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you were detained,\Nmurders by Kira stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Ryuzaki, hear me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:32.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not lying... I'm not Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only think\Nthat I've been framed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong...Light Yagami-?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're saying doesn't\Nmake sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:43.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...for some reason it feels\Nlike it's the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:47.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get me out of here.\NWe're wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I can't let you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:53.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... How did this happen-?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:56.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NThis isn't like Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:19:00.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking back what he said earlier.\NIt makes no logical sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:05.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't release him now\Nthat the murders have stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:10.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever anyone says...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:13.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,can't we just decide that\NLight Yagami is Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and that the case is solved?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:20.79,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,558)}Fifteenth Day of Confinement
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:21.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:26.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two weeks worth of criminals\Nwere murdered all at once yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira Strikes Again\NKira is back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell the Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:32.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:36.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, Kira has started killing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:37.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:42.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira was just resting.\NHe's started punishing criminals again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Matsuda-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:46.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:50.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be happy that\Nthe murders have occurred, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,now, suspicion of my son will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...knowing Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't say he's completely\Ncleared just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:01.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:02.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the grey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:04.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that, Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he was pretty much\Nguilty up to now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:11.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a grey that's\None shade closer to being clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:12.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll tell Light, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:15.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda! I mean, Mr. Matsuda,\Nplease stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:16.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:21.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why-?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:23.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:30.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been over two weeks.\NThere haven't been any new killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:34.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you just give up and\Nconfess that you're Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say stupid things\Nlike that, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:37.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:42.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why you deduced from\Nthe investigation that I'm Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:43.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:48.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Kira! Zoom in or something\Nand look at my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these the eyes of\Nsomeone who's lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:59.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane...you're really sure that\Nyou don't know who Kira is, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:04.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That again?\NThat's what I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is a hero of justice who
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:10.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,punished the burglar who\Nkilled my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:19.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:29.46,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:34.85,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:43.85,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:50.28,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:54.82,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:22:00.54,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:08.00,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:13.18,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:23.94,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
